Hmm, the modifiers are being applied to `total` (policyBase + itemSpecificSurcharges), not just to `policyBase`. But the spec says policy-wide modifiers apply to "the policy base premium (the sum of all item base premiums)".

So the policy-wide modifiers should be applied to `policyBase` only, not to `total` (which includes item-specific surcharges).

